LOCUS       pTNos:BASTA:PNos_(GB0023) 4205 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Provides the bar gene for resistance to basta fused to the A.
            tumefaciens Nopaline synthase promoter and terminator. Cloned as a
            level 0 GB part ready to be transferred to a GB level1 plant
            expression vector..
